title: Make The Switch
itunes:title: Make The Switch
description:
You don’t have to live with sickness, addiction or oppression. God wants to heal you! Make the switch from wondering if it is His will for you to be healthy and whole to believing that He wants to bless you. Your attitude should be, “God, I receive Your healing. I know You carried this sickness so I don’t have to.”

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
